  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">An engineer wanted to identify the best angle for a cooling fan in an engine in order to get the greatest airflow. The engineer discovered that the function above models the airflow <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of theta\"></span></span>, in cubic feet per minute, as a function of the angle of the fan <span class=\"italic\"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"theta\"></span></span>, in degrees. According to the model, what angle, in degrees, gives the greatest airflow?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph \">&ndash;0.28</p>\n"
